{"core_case_metadata": {"authoritative_case_number": "117/2026", "authoritative_decision_date": "19/03/2026", "court": "澳門法院", "language": "zh", "case_type": "刑事訴訟程序的上訴", "pdf_url": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh-42996a25f2078357.pdf", "text_url_or_action": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh/42293", "source_chunk_ids": ["117_2026_zh_c0000_96b2baf322bb", "117_2026_zh_c0001_1779ea03cd41", "117_2026_zh_c0002_171a5b46e667", "117_2026_zh_c0003_3d9617c60a28", "117_2026_zh_c0004_a8afceba8d06", "117_2026_zh_c0005_cf382f5d6bbe", "117_2026_zh_c0006_ef3b69cf46d8"], "source_case_paths": ["cases/zh/2026/117_2026/full_text.txt", "cases/zh/2026/117_2026/metadata.json"]}, "generated_digest_metadata": {"case_summary": "上訴人因違反交通紅燈管制被判處禁止駕駛及吊銷駕駛執照的附加刑。上訴人認為原審法院未考慮暫緩執行吊銷駕駛執照的機制，並對其家庭造成毀滅性影響。本院認同檢察院見解，認為暫緩執行僅屬例外情況。", "holding": "裁定上訴人A的上訴理由不成立，維持原判。", "legal_basis": ["第3/2007號法律《道路交通法》第108條第1款", "第3/2007號法律《道路交通法》第109條第1款"], "disputed_issues": ["暫緩執行吊銷駕駛執照的附加刑", "原審法院是否考慮了上訴人的家庭狀況及工作需要"]}, "generation_status": "local_model_generated", "generation_method": "local_model_generated", "model_name": "qwen2.5:3b-instruct", "prompt_version": "day45_prompt_b_tch_norm", "script_normalization_applied": false, "output_script": "traditional_chinese", "provenance_notes": ["Local-only generation path.", "No cloud API/database used.", "backend=ollama_cli"]}
{"core_case_metadata": {"authoritative_case_number": "118/2026", "authoritative_decision_date": "12/03/2026", "court": "澳門法院", "language": "zh", "case_type": "刑事訴訟程序的上訴", "pdf_url": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh-cb01720a40c0c32b.pdf", "text_url_or_action": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh/42289", "source_chunk_ids": ["118_2026_zh_c0000_1d525ba05add", "118_2026_zh_c0001_55849ff34d62", "118_2026_zh_c0002_174e545b1bdb", "118_2026_zh_c0003_16d79635bc21", "118_2026_zh_c0004_78c14c173c48", "118_2026_zh_c0005_2414003aa142", "118_2026_zh_c0006_9e8aeaffd320", "118_2026_zh_c0007_d90881761ab7", "118_2026_zh_c0008_d3359698211e", "118_2026_zh_c0009_63bb5ac8b8fb"], "source_case_paths": ["cases/zh/2026/118_2026/full_text.txt", "cases/zh/2026/118_2026/metadata.json"]}, "generated_digest_metadata": {"case_summary": "上訴人A對初級法院的判決不服，提出上訴，主要爭點在於審查證據方面明顯有錯誤及適用法律的錯誤。原審法院認定上訴人A以直接正犯、故意及既遂的方式觸犯第17/2009號法律第11條第1款第1項所規定及處罰的一項較輕量販賣罪，判處1年9個月的實際徒刑。上訴人提出審查證據方面明顯有錯誤，以及適用存疑從無原則等理據，要求改判控訴事實不獲證實，或廢止原判決。", "holding": "本院裁定上訴人A的上訴理由均不成立，維持原審判決。", "legal_basis": ["《刑法典》第9條、第12條、第25條、第17/2009號法律第11條第1款第1項", "《刑事訴訟法典》第400條第2款c項"], "disputed_issues": ["審查證據方面明顯有錯誤", "適用法律的錯誤"]}, "generation_status": "local_model_generated", "generation_method": "local_model_generated", "model_name": "qwen2.5:3b-instruct", "prompt_version": "day45_prompt_b_tch_norm", "script_normalization_applied": false, "output_script": "traditional_chinese", "provenance_notes": ["Local-only generation path.", "No cloud API/database used.", "backend=ollama_cli"]}
{"core_case_metadata": {"authoritative_case_number": "119/2026", "authoritative_decision_date": "26/02/2026", "court": "澳門法院", "language": "zh", "case_type": "刑事訴訟程序的上訴", "pdf_url": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh-f8263615c6b52a59.pdf", "text_url_or_action": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh/42283", "source_chunk_ids": ["119_2026_zh_c0000_6d5f59d7a55f", "119_2026_zh_c0001_79fb9c101360", "119_2026_zh_c0002_fa1b422a323f", "119_2026_zh_c0003_1a17edc209e4", "119_2026_zh_c0004_efca5d5ef499", "119_2026_zh_c0005_fc4c5f76bb84", "119_2026_zh_c0006_06b56d918974", "119_2026_zh_c0007_d58d270ac064"], "source_case_paths": ["cases/zh/2026/119_2026/full_text.txt", "cases/zh/2026/119_2026/metadata.json"]}, "generated_digest_metadata": {"case_summary": "澳門初級法院刑事起訴法庭在PLC-034-17-2-A案中，因上訴人A不符合《刑法典》第56條的假釋實質要件，於2025年12月19日否決其假釋申請。上訴人不服，向澳門中級法院提出上訴。合議庭裁定維持原判。", "holding": "合議庭認為上訴人A不符合《刑法典》第56條的假釋實質要件，因此維持了刑事起訴法庭的決定。", "legal_basis": ["《刑法典》第56條"], "disputed_issues": ["假釋的實質要件", "特別預防和一般預防的要求"]}, "generation_status": "local_model_generated", "generation_method": "local_model_generated", "model_name": "qwen2.5:3b-instruct", "prompt_version": "day45_prompt_b_tch_norm", "script_normalization_applied": false, "output_script": "traditional_chinese", "provenance_notes": ["Local-only generation path.", "No cloud API/database used.", "backend=ollama_cli"]}
{"core_case_metadata": {"authoritative_case_number": "120/2026", "authoritative_decision_date": "26/02/2026", "court": "澳門法院", "language": "zh", "case_type": "刑事訴訟程序的上訴", "pdf_url": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh-2583593f6cf11801.pdf", "text_url_or_action": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh/42281", "source_chunk_ids": ["120_2026_zh_c0000_2e47381d8f27", "120_2026_zh_c0001_5fd5f39a66f1", "120_2026_zh_c0002_8b9c8bcd3c6a", "120_2026_zh_c0003_62be53b50a94", "120_2026_zh_c0004_c95f61066128", "120_2026_zh_c0005_4611e2f57c44", "120_2026_zh_c0006_739154402df5", "120_2026_zh_c0007_5cf85b301992", "120_2026_zh_c0008_bb327b06b668", "120_2026_zh_c0009_68fa17a691ac"], "source_case_paths": ["cases/zh/2026/120_2026/full_text.txt", "cases/zh/2026/120_2026/metadata.json"]}, "generated_digest_metadata": {"case_summary": "上訴人A因犯‘巨額詐騙罪’和‘相當巨額詐騙罪’被判刑三年三個月，並被要求賠償兩名被害人共計人民幣279,300元。在案件審理期間，上訴人未支付訴訟費用及賠償金，但已申請分期付款並獲得批准。上訴人表現出良好的行爲表現和積極的悔改態度，包括參加職業培訓、與家人保持聯繫等。", "holding": "合議庭否決了上訴人的假釋請求，認爲其不符合《刑法典》第56條規定的實質要件。具體來說，合議庭認爲上訴人雖然表現出良好的行爲表現和悔改態度，但未支付賠償金的行爲不利於一般預防和社會安寧的維護。", "legal_basis": ["刑法典 第56條"], "disputed_issues": ["假釋的實質要件"]}, "generation_status": "local_model_generated", "generation_method": "local_model_generated", "model_name": "qwen2.5:3b-instruct", "prompt_version": "day45_prompt_b_tch_norm", "script_normalization_applied": true, "output_script": "traditional_chinese", "provenance_notes": ["Local-only generation path.", "No cloud API/database used.", "backend=ollama_cli"]}
{"core_case_metadata": {"authoritative_case_number": "123/2026", "authoritative_decision_date": "12/03/2026", "court": "澳門法院", "language": "zh", "case_type": "刑事訴訟程序的上訴", "pdf_url": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh-c71f1f7af3f30288.pdf", "text_url_or_action": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh/42319", "source_chunk_ids": ["123_2026_zh_c0000_574efcf25448", "123_2026_zh_c0001_8bc195419e38", "123_2026_zh_c0002_f4fc952e1178", "123_2026_zh_c0003_ab90b8acbea1", "123_2026_zh_c0004_d5e6bf5b722e", "123_2026_zh_c0005_6d7682e1f2c9", "123_2026_zh_c0006_fed0889265e7", "123_2026_zh_c0007_107000322f6a"], "source_case_paths": ["cases/zh/2026/123_2026/full_text.txt", "cases/zh/2026/123_2026/metadata.json"]}, "generated_digest_metadata": {"case_summary": "聲明異議人A對刑事起訴法庭否決其假釋上訴的裁決提出聲明異議。主要理由是認為自己符合假釋條件，並指出了判決中的錯誤和不當之處。裁判書製作人在簡要裁判中認同了上訴人在近一年行為有所改善，但考慮到曾多次在獄中違規，僅憑近期表現不足以判斷其能否誠實生活不再犯罪。最終裁定聲明異議人的聲明異議理由不成立。", "holding": "聲明異議人的聲明異議理由並不成立。", "legal_basis": ["《刑事訴訟法典》第407條第6款", "《刑法典》第56條第1款"], "disputed_issues": ["假釋的適用條件", "上訴人近期表現是否足以判斷其能否誠實生活不再犯罪"]}, "generation_status": "local_model_generated", "generation_method": "local_model_generated", "model_name": "qwen2.5:3b-instruct", "prompt_version": "day45_prompt_b_tch_norm", "script_normalization_applied": false, "output_script": "traditional_chinese", "provenance_notes": ["Local-only generation path.", "No cloud API/database used.", "backend=ollama_cli"]}
{"core_case_metadata": {"authoritative_case_number": "136/2025", "authoritative_decision_date": "26/02/2026", "court": "澳門法院", "language": "zh", "case_type": "行政, 稅務及海關方面的司法裁判的上訴", "pdf_url": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh-6158f91c1c76bb04.pdf", "text_url_or_action": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh/42191", "source_chunk_ids": ["136_2025_zh_c0000_529ac7a04c8f", "136_2025_zh_c0001_24f4331d6d9c", "136_2025_zh_c0002_d8ad3058cee4", "136_2025_zh_c0003_a6bae73bd557", "136_2025_zh_c0004_a5f8873f3608", "136_2025_zh_c0005_b7bcb0f694ad", "136_2025_zh_c0006_b0925c1087af", "136_2025_zh_c0007_6eed5683ea02", "136_2025_zh_c0008_97d94bf6fe13", "136_2025_zh_c0009_97c025905ebd", "136_2025_zh_c0010_92a05774eab5", "136_2025_zh_c0011_a650c580aba2", "136_2025_zh_c0012_2a0860e05d25", "136_2025_zh_c0013_6698348a20dc", "136_2025_zh_c0014_a7580e196528"], "source_case_paths": ["cases/zh/2026/136_2025/full_text.txt", "cases/zh/2026/136_2025/metadata.json"]}, "generated_digest_metadata": {"case_summary": "上訴案第136/2025號，涉及交通事務局局長對駕駛學校校長的處罰決定。被上訴人A因不服該決定提起上訴，主張原審法院錯誤解釋及適用《道路交通規章》第102條第1款結合第4款b)項之規定，認為駕駛學校校長違反職責並受懲罰。", "holding": "本院認同被上訴判決，駕駛學校校長的行為不符合《道路交通規章》第102條第4款b)項所規定的“嚴重或反覆不認識、疏忽或不履行職責”的要求。因此，駕駛學校校長未違反該規定。", "legal_basis": ["《道路交通規章》第102條第1款", "《道路交通規章》第102條第4款b)項"], "disputed_issues": ["駕駛學校校長的行為是否符合《道路交通規章》第102條第4款b)項所規定的‘嚴重或反覆不認識、疏忽或不履行職責’的要求"]}, "generation_status": "local_model_generated", "generation_method": "local_model_generated", "model_name": "qwen2.5:3b-instruct", "prompt_version": "day45_prompt_b_tch_norm", "script_normalization_applied": false, "output_script": "traditional_chinese", "provenance_notes": ["Local-only generation path.", "No cloud API/database used.", "backend=ollama_cli"]}
{"core_case_metadata": {"authoritative_case_number": "137/2026", "authoritative_decision_date": "26/02/2026", "court": "澳門法院", "language": "zh", "case_type": "刑事訴訟程序的上訴", "pdf_url": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh-afc4df457d48b2bd.pdf", "text_url_or_action": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh/42265", "source_chunk_ids": ["137_2026_zh_c0000_37f07609489c", "137_2026_zh_c0001_61e0949c968b", "137_2026_zh_c0002_c65ea2e60257", "137_2026_zh_c0003_cfddb5440d12", "137_2026_zh_c0004_ae937d7d4907", "137_2026_zh_c0005_dc5437de5d66", "137_2026_zh_c0006_26b1766a3746", "137_2026_zh_c0007_02a2ae128218"], "source_case_paths": ["cases/zh/2026/137_2026/full_text.txt", "cases/zh/2026/137_2026/metadata.json"]}, "generated_digest_metadata": {"case_summary": "上訴人A因詐騙罪被判刑，現已服刑期的三分之二且超過六個月。上訴人提出假釋申請，理由包括服刑表現良好、家庭支持及工作安排等。刑事起訴法庭否決了假釋申請，認為上訴人尚未符合《刑法典》第56條第1款a項和b項的要件。", "holding": "本上訴法院認為，原審判決未違反澳門《刑法典》第56條第1款a)及b)項規定，應予以維持。", "legal_basis": ["《刑法典》第56條"], "disputed_issues": ["假釋的實質要件", "特別預防和一般預防需要"]}, "generation_status": "local_model_generated", "generation_method": "local_model_generated", "model_name": "qwen2.5:3b-instruct", "prompt_version": "day45_prompt_b_tch_norm", "script_normalization_applied": false, "output_script": "traditional_chinese", "provenance_notes": ["Local-only generation path.", "No cloud API/database used.", "backend=ollama_cli"]}
{"core_case_metadata": {"authoritative_case_number": "145/2026", "authoritative_decision_date": "26/02/2026", "court": "澳門法院", "language": "zh", "case_type": "刑事訴訟程序的上訴", "pdf_url": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh-d65744fe0f28dc49.pdf", "text_url_or_action": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh/42259", "source_chunk_ids": ["145_2026_zh_c0000_f9e82a7592e0", "145_2026_zh_c0001_0511b9b99c06", "145_2026_zh_c0002_cb199e663da7", "145_2026_zh_c0003_085a5bdabb5b", "145_2026_zh_c0004_f78f223f2f8d"], "source_case_paths": ["cases/zh/2026/145_2026/full_text.txt", "cases/zh/2026/145_2026/metadata.json"]}, "generated_digest_metadata": {"case_summary": "上訴人A因犯有相當巨額詐騙罪，被判兩年實際徒刑。在服刑期間，A已繳付所有訴訟費用及其他負擔，並於2026年8月19日服滿刑期的三分之二。A曾違反獄規被處罰一次，但其父母持續探訪，家人亦有聯繫。A表示出獄後將返回香港與家人同住，工作方面會繼續經營髮型屋及網上水族店。刑事起訴法庭於2025年12月19日不批准A的假釋申請，理由是A在服刑期間表現一般，且其犯罪行為對社會造成負面影響。本院接受上訴人提起的上訴後，認為A不符合《刑法典》第56條第1款a)項及b)項所規定的假釋條件。", "holding": "裁判書製作人裁定上訴人的上訴理由明顯不成立，予以駁回。判處上訴人繳付3個計算單位之司法費，上訴的訴訟費用。", "legal_basis": ["《刑法典》第56條第1款"], "disputed_issues": ["是否符合假釋條件"]}, "generation_status": "local_model_generated", "generation_method": "local_model_generated", "model_name": "qwen2.5:3b-instruct", "prompt_version": "day45_prompt_b_tch_norm", "script_normalization_applied": false, "output_script": "traditional_chinese", "provenance_notes": ["Local-only generation path.", "No cloud API/database used.", "backend=ollama_cli"]}
{"core_case_metadata": {"authoritative_case_number": "147/2025", "authoritative_decision_date": "12/03/2026", "court": "澳門法院", "language": "zh", "case_type": "刑事訴訟程序的上訴", "pdf_url": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh-e646b54075142674.pdf", "text_url_or_action": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh/42291", "source_chunk_ids": ["147_2025_zh_c0000_ca024a010310", "147_2025_zh_c0001_d029b75aff78", "147_2025_zh_c0002_1b541d2e65cb", "147_2025_zh_c0003_bb4a1e30bb4e", "147_2025_zh_c0004_c4aa5499b063", "147_2025_zh_c0005_de240a56fc4a", "147_2025_zh_c0006_d0b3f4c14508", "147_2025_zh_c0007_c4fa6f96ff71", "147_2025_zh_c0008_3b68b8cf38f0", "147_2025_zh_c0009_ddbab538c767", "147_2025_zh_c0010_f300d8fcacfc", "147_2025_zh_c0011_b1fa3fa8fd63", "147_2025_zh_c0012_cd8849e8a1cf", "147_2025_zh_c0013_4a471d1c6604", "147_2025_zh_c0014_7ca00464c9e2"], "source_case_paths": ["cases/zh/2026/147_2025/full_text.txt", "cases/zh/2026/147_2025/metadata.json"]}, "generated_digest_metadata": {"case_summary": "上訴人A對初級法院的判決提起上訴，主要針對原審法院在緩刑義務設定上的理解錯誤和過度審理。原審法院裁定上訴人須在判決確定後兩個月內向被害人支付壹拾萬澳門元作為慰問金，以彌補犯罪惡害。上訴人認為此判決存在法律理解錯誤及過度審理的瑕疵。", "holding": "合議庭裁定上訴人的上訴理由不成立，維持原審裁決。", "legal_basis": ["刑法典第48條", "刑法典第49條"], "disputed_issues": ["理解法律錯誤", "過度審理"]}, "generation_status": "local_model_generated", "generation_method": "local_model_generated", "model_name": "qwen2.5:3b-instruct", "prompt_version": "day45_prompt_b_tch_norm", "script_normalization_applied": false, "output_script": "traditional_chinese", "provenance_notes": ["Local-only generation path.", "No cloud API/database used.", "backend=ollama_cli"]}
{"core_case_metadata": {"authoritative_case_number": "151/2026", "authoritative_decision_date": "12/03/2026", "court": "澳門法院", "language": "zh", "case_type": "刑事訴訟程序的上訴", "pdf_url": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh-c409775ab76054ae.pdf", "text_url_or_action": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh/42387", "source_chunk_ids": ["151_2026_zh_c0000_e1bb7733c024", "151_2026_zh_c0001_a8ebafba164b", "151_2026_zh_c0002_e92fc3b94090", "151_2026_zh_c0003_ffa5ff197b6a", "151_2026_zh_c0004_383b6f02b566", "151_2026_zh_c0005_c33570656445", "151_2026_zh_c0006_8cb7ae106537", "151_2026_zh_c0007_23d297a28395", "151_2026_zh_c0008_7cf0fe8c37fa", "151_2026_zh_c0009_32045e593a7f", "151_2026_zh_c0010_2cd652679e3d", "151_2026_zh_c0011_2b8df73f765a", "151_2026_zh_c0012_9f188fc31c1c", "151_2026_zh_c0013_98c9f6ae8fd4", "151_2026_zh_c0014_829e5a2f1568", "151_2026_zh_c0015_02ffd0fa9d61", "151_2026_zh_c0016_3ce5edf8815c", "151_2026_zh_c0017_3c621b8b2614", "151_2026_zh_c0018_7b2caf1667a1"], "source_case_paths": ["cases/zh/2026/151_2026/full_text.txt", "cases/zh/2026/151_2026/metadata.json"]}, "generated_digest_metadata": {"case_summary": "上訴人(A)對刑事上訴案提出上訴，主要問題包括審查證據錯誤、已證事實不足以支持裁判、吸毒罪的吸收、量刑過重等。原審法院認定上訴人觸犯了不法販賣麻醉藥品及精神藥物罪、不法吸食麻醉藥品及精神藥物罪和抗拒及脅迫罪，並判處六年實際徒刑。上訴人主張審查證據錯誤、已證事實不足以支持裁判、應將對上訴人的販賣毒品罪吸收其吸食毒品罪、量刑過重等。", "holding": "本院裁定上訴人(A)的上訴理由部分成立，廢止原審法院對上訴人所判處的一項不法吸食麻醉藥品及精神藥物罪，並應就該項控罪對上訴人作出開釋。針對上訴人所觸犯的一項不法販賣麻醉藥品及精神藥物罪及抗拒及脅迫罪，兩罪並罰，合共改判上訴人5年10個月實際徒刑的單一刑罰。", "legal_basis": ["第17/2009號法律（經第4/2014號法律、第10/2016號法律、第10/2019號法律、第22/2020號法律、第10/2021號法律、第18/2023號法律及第16/2024號法律所修改）第8條第1款", "第17/2009號法律（經第4/2014號法律、第10/2016號法律、第10/2019號法律、第22/2020號法律、第10/2021號法律、第18/2023號法律及第16/2024號法律所修改）第14條第1款", "澳門《刑法典》第311條"], "disputed_issues": ["審查證據錯誤", "已證事實不足以支持裁判", "應將對上訴人的販賣毒品罪吸收其吸食毒品罪", "量刑過重"]}, "generation_status": "local_model_generated", "generation_method": "local_model_generated", "model_name": "qwen2.5:3b-instruct", "prompt_version": "day45_prompt_b_tch_norm", "script_normalization_applied": false, "output_script": "traditional_chinese", "provenance_notes": ["Local-only generation path.", "No cloud API/database used.", "backend=ollama_cli"]}
