{"core_case_metadata": {"authoritative_case_number": "164/2026", "authoritative_decision_date": "26/02/2026", "court": "澳門法院", "language": "zh", "case_type": "刑事訴訟程序的上訴", "pdf_url": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh-f9a8bc453cbfc6f5.pdf", "text_url_or_action": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh/42261", "source_chunk_ids": ["164_2026_zh_c0000_d32ea2c18b0c", "164_2026_zh_c0001_03708a419682", "164_2026_zh_c0002_4c9f08678fd1", "164_2026_zh_c0003_a324f477dfc0", "164_2026_zh_c0004_5d9130c79e2c", "164_2026_zh_c0005_46928179b707"], "source_case_paths": ["cases/zh/2026/164_2026/full_text.txt", "cases/zh/2026/164_2026/metadata.json"]}, "generated_digest_metadata": {"case_summary": "上訴人A因觸犯詐騙罪被判一年實際徒刑。在假釋申請被初級法院否決後，A向本中級法院提出上訴，主張其已符合假釋條件，請求廢止原審判決並批准其假釋。然而，檢察院認為A不符合假釋的實質要件，包括未支付賠償金、未參與學習活動及職業培訓等，因此駁回了上訴。", "holding": "本中級法院接納檢察院之建議，否決囚犯A之假釋聲請。", "legal_basis": ["《刑法典》第56條"], "disputed_issues": ["未支付被判處的訴訟費用", "未向被害人作出賠償", "沒有參與獄方舉辦的課程及職業培訓", "未能為其重返社會做準備"]}, "generation_status": "local_model_generated", "generation_method": "local_model_generated", "model_name": "qwen2.5:3b-instruct", "prompt_version": "day45_prompt_b_tch_norm", "script_normalization_applied": false, "output_script": "traditional_chinese", "provenance_notes": ["Local-only generation path.", "No cloud API/database used.", "backend=ollama_cli"]}
