{"core_case_metadata": {"authoritative_case_number": "206/2026", "authoritative_decision_date": "24/03/2026", "court": "澳門法院", "language": "zh", "case_type": "刑事訴訟程序的上訴", "pdf_url": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh-cedacb52acdf7fa2.pdf", "text_url_or_action": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh/42351", "source_chunk_ids": ["206_2026_zh_c0000_bc0c17c0df83", "206_2026_zh_c0001_d635599d1b1d", "206_2026_zh_c0002_75ebac61958e", "206_2026_zh_c0003_4e536d06ea79", "206_2026_zh_c0004_3d620bcc0102", "206_2026_zh_c0005_868ffdb12de9", "206_2026_zh_c0006_57bdfc3f8667", "206_2026_zh_c0007_a7035a6a4591", "206_2026_zh_c0008_7969693b5d78"], "source_case_paths": ["cases/zh/2026/206_2026/full_text.txt", "cases/zh/2026/206_2026/metadata.json"]}, "generated_digest_metadata": {"case_summary": "上訴人A因多次觸犯賭場相關犯罪被判刑，且在監獄中表現不佳。上訴人認為其已改過自新，請求批准假釋。然而，法院考慮到其多次違法行為、缺乏積極改造表現及對社會的負面影響，否決了上訴。", "holding": "本法庭認為上訴人仍未符合《刑法典》第56條第1款a）項和b）項所規定的假釋條件，因此否決上訴人的假釋申請。", "legal_basis": ["《刑法典》第56條第1款a)項（特別要件）", "《刑法典》第56條第1款b)項（一般要件）"], "disputed_issues": ["上訴人是否已改過自新，能否以堅定的意志重新做人、遵紀守法並負責任地生活。", "提前釋放上訴人會否使公眾在心理上無法承受以及對社會秩序產生衝擊。"]}, "generation_status": "local_model_generated", "generation_method": "local_model_generated", "model_name": "qwen2.5:3b-instruct", "prompt_version": "day45_prompt_b_tch_norm", "script_normalization_applied": false, "output_script": "traditional_chinese", "provenance_notes": ["Local-only generation path.", "No cloud API/database used.", "backend=ollama_cli"]}
